{
  "stem": "14429.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He was told, and he had to sign papers, that he can never return back to Aachen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The three of us had to leave back to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I went back to the orphanage, and my brothers and my father, I don't remember where they stayed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But maybe with my uncle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Because my uncle, I know, had affidavit to go to Palestine with his family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] A month later, Leon said to Papa, Papa, Norbert and I are going over the border by ourselves.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I'm not staying here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But then, they were 14 and 16.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] At-- but at the time, my uncle also went to Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I think he also tried to go illegally to Belgium first.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he said he's going to go with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They are going to go with them, so they're not alone, but they are going over the border by themselves.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Sure enough, Leon and Norbert took a guide and crossed the border by themselves into Belgium.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Two kids.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "My father could not leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "He had to see what's going to be with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "My brothers then put actions in motion with the Belgian government to get me out legally.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And it finally was agreed by the German government and Belgian government that the childrens' transport is going to go out from Austria to Belgium, and I was among the children.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "When that was assured, my father, again, went illegally over the border.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Oh, by the way, before I forget.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "When we went to first illegally to the border, and we were caught, my father had to throw away his money that he had.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
